## ✨ Features

- 🎨 **Unified Design Language** — blends material smoothness, fluent shapes, and apple-like elegance  
- ⚙️ **200+ Lines of CSS** — ready-to-use components, utilities, and responsive layouts  
- 💡 **No Dependencies** — pure CSS, zero JS required  
- 📱 **Responsive & Adaptive** — mobile-first design  
- 🌙 **Light & Dark Themes** built in  
- 🧱 **Utilities for Everything** — spacing, grids, flex, typography, shadows, and animations  
- ⚡ **Production-Ready CDN** support (via cdnjs, jsDelivr, or your own host)

